&lt;li&gt;Experience managing and closing large-scale deals (e.g., $1M+ contracts) with major retailers or companies of similar scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong ability to generate and manage a highly detailed and organized pipeline of enterprise sales opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
