&lt;p data-start=&quot;715&quot; data-end=&quot;1031&quot;&gt;As Senior Manager, Corporate IT, you will lead the function responsible for delivering secure, reliable and modern technology experiences to Zipsters across Australia and New Zealand. This is an opportunity to shape the strategy, operating model and employee technology experience that powers our business every day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1033&quot; data-end=&quot;1527&quot;&gt;Combining strategic leadership with hands on operational excellence, you will partner closely with leaders across Technology, Security, People &amp;amp; Culture and Finance to drive innovation, strengthen governance and create technology experiences that help our people do their best work. From workplace technology and enterprise applications through to automation, AI adoption and technology procurement, your impact will be felt across the entire organisation.&lt;/p&gt;
